{
  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "According to the Law of Ukraine dated 22.10.1993 No.",
    "3551-XII, \"On the status of war veterans, guarantees of their social protection\" (Current version 16.01.2024.",
    "), war veterans are individuals who participated in the defense of the Motherland or hostilities on the territory of other of states.",
    "War veterans also include: combatants, people with disabilities as a result of war, war participants.",
    "In general, according to the specified law with numerous point changes in its provisions, this word unites 54 categories of citizens who have the status of a war veteran and are covered under state benefits and guarantees."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "According to the Law of Ukraine dated 22.10.1993 No."
  ]
}